Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From when I was little,\NI had a question in my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I only myself, and not someone else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard that "I think, therefore I am"\Nare the words of an ancient philosopher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I didn't think.\NI thought about someone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That perhaps, the person over there\Nis myself as well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:59.14,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1\N"I think about others"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:01:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Think about others."\NWhen I did that, I had turned into someone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But no more than five seconds.\NAfter that, I immediately returned to my own self.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, for the duration,\Nmy body completely loses consciousness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Often I would find myself \Ninjured in some way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, I can only possess someone\Nthat is within my line of sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, I couldn't use it for lewd things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At most, it was for possessing someone\Nthat pissed me off,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}only to pick a fight with a stranger\Nthen return to myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kind of retaliation was \Nall I could use this for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What do you \Nthink you just did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But finally, I came up with an idea\Nthat can take full advantage of this special ability.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes before time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could possess one smart guy in class\Nafter another, memorize the answers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}memorize the answers, and fill in my answers\Nafter returning... and I repeat that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Year-End Test Standings\N1 - Yu Otosaka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, I'm planning on attending\Na very prestigious high school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, unlike a normal test, I don't know\Nwho is intelligent during an entrance exam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since, I've snuck into\Nprestigious cram schools one after another,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}pretending to be a student \Nof that cram school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which student facing entrance exams\Napply to which schools?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And which subjects were they best at?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I researched all of that very thoroughly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.45,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High School\NEntrance Exam Venue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I found one student after another that\Nwas vying to enter the same school as I was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And successfully got admitted \Nto an elite high school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:59.13,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, a word from the representative\Nfor the new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu Otosaka, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that means he's the top of the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he's good-looking to boot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today, for us new students, you have organized\Na grand ceremony of this sort,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we are deeply in gratitude for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wrapped in the warm rays \Nof the spring sunshine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are now able to be a part\Nof the well-established ranks of Hinomori High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.03,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.16,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he attractive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he might be your type, Mitchon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Yumi doesn't seem\Nto be against the idea either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are very grateful for \Nthis opportunity today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Previous Term Class Ranking\N1 - Yu Otosaka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.74,Copy of OS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the sudden email:\NMy name is Sugimoto from Class 1-2.\NWill you possibly come to the back\Nof the school building after school?\NI will be waiting for you till the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stuff like this is happening more often.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only am I superior\Nas the top of the class academically,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm one of the more physically attractive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible to not be \Npopular among girls like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sheesh, I'll hurry them all on home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you \Nover all the way out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. What did you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm fine from starting as just friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But can you think about dating me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... In order to keep my grades up\Nat where they are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to shave time to \Nsleep to keep studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the luxury\Nof dealing with other people. So, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course that's a pack of lies.\NI don't study whatsoever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I understand.\NI'm sorry for calling you out like this so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I would choose \Nnormal girls like you ilk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one I'm after...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Yumi, you missed\Nthe special program from yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, is the madonna of this school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yumi Shirayanagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...make you mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I will definitely get a chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all lies in how I use the five seconds,\Nwhich are the limits of my ability!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:21.57,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I was texting until 3 o'clock last night,\Nso I overslept... it was so hard for me to get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mitchon, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looks like he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was close, but that \Nwent according to plan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi, you were about to be run over by a truck\Nwhen Otosaka from class 1 saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the nurse's office. Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us were about to go eat\Nour favorite pancakes together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,would you like to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to pass.\NIt's better to keep that among friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, you just saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to properly repay that,\Nand I'd like to chat with you a little while longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I have a call. Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll go home. Yup, yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mitchon, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother suddenly came back from Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he apparently ordered\Ntop-end sushi for the entire family!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm leaving the rest \Nto the two of you! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was an obvious farce,\Nbut a nice assist nonetheless, Mitchon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's a special way to eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please mimic me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you do this, the syrup\Ngets across to the entire thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, stack them up, cut \Nthem, and try a bite of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Just by changing how you eat it,\Nit gets this delicious? I never knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I \Neat this, it's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The song they're playing right now\Nis Haro-haro, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haro-haro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know of them?\NI had thought every boy knew of them very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So something like them is popular nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, can we go home\Ntogether from school
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or have an occasional meal together\Nlike this again sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go home together today as well?\NI will be waiting for you near the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I shouldn't do this out loud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I'll hurry on over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:51.49,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yu Otosaka from class 1-1, please report immediately\Nto the student council room. I repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:56.24,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yu Otosaka from class 1-1, please report immediately\Nto the student council room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:56.24,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-Sorry, I will be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.62,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-Sorry, I will be late.\N-I will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Omura, the student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with me? I'm making someone\Nwait, so I'd like you to make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is really up to you. This is a copy of your\Nanswer sheet to the aptitude test from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect score... so marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same exact test has \Nbeen placed right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, right now, please try\Nto get a perfect score once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What meaning is there behind that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is an accusation\Nthat you may have cheated on the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can get 90% or above, you are innocent.\NYou will be deemed guilty if your score is any lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is absurd! I will \Nexcuse myself right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning this case, we have the authorization\Nof both the principal and the vice-principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you escape now, you will apparently\Nbe expelled from the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-Expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right there lies all of the answers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll possess him and find out!\NThat's the only way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making such a fool of me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it only seemed like \Nyou were tearing that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there, I'm Tomori, the student\Ncouncil president... of another school, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was recording you for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take a look at the \Nvideo I just recorded?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a note of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were not looking at him\Nthe moment he ripped the answer sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you said he ripped it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a special ability \Nto possess other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Using that, you cheat on every exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not true!\NIt's a sleeping disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly get tremendously sleepy,\Nand can't fight that urge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:11:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a troublesome one.\NI'll show you this now. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A copy of your medical exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As far as this goes, such \Na disease doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please solve the problems on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a farce! I can't deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... she had foreseen\Nthat it would even end up this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everything from here on is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is going on here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You... what the hell did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just like it sounds, I teleport instantly\Nto move to another location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this ability doesn't let me\Nconveniently stop exactly where I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this ability, I don't know\Nhow many times I've been hospitalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an incomplete ability!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, what are you\Ngoing to do with me from now on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will have you transfer over to our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In this world, there are many people\Nwho possess special powers, not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, those special skills can be considered\Nan illness caught during adolescence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and will disappear in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until it goes away, however, please keep commuting\Nto our school, the Hoshinoumi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I already have gotten permission from those\Nthat have parental authority over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a story...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However... you seem like you'd be popular\Nfrom just your looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was there also a need to play the role of a genius\Nby cheating as much as possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but thanks to that\Nyou were able to close the gap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between yourself and the female student\Nyou were targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What... she disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is her ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... an ability \Nto become invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. To me, it only looked \Nlike her punching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:15:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... I was the only one\Nthat couldn't see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Her ability is to hide from\Nvisual recognition from one target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every other human can see her as normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another imperfect ability!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you will enter\Nour student council as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability is useful,\Nso I'd like you to cooperate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To threaten those that abuse their powers\Nfor no good, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the kind of existence we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Big Brother Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wow! What's wrong with your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, um... it was an \Nincident during gym class...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, there was\Nan amazing phone call from our uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu heard that she and Big Brother Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will transfer into Hoshinoumi Academy's\Nmiddle- and high-school
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as scholarship students!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you serious?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The house budget will benefit from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the uncle is sending us\Nlots of tasty food to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that means\Nyou have to transfer schools, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means you have to say goodbye\Nto your friends - is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays we can use smartphones to chat\Nwhile looking at each other's faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so it's not going to be all that lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:21.60,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshinoumi Academy\NExecutive Office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's dinner is... ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.98,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Omelet rice, your favorite \Ndish, Big Brother Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This again? I said time and again\Nthat it was only when I was little...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats! Now, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So sweet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using pizza sauce as the secret ingredient must\Nhave been fitting for my tongue when I was a child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat Mom's omelet rice\Nfor the first time in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, huh? Who cares about someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am... She got divorced,\Nand selfishly shoved custody over to our uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu doesn't understand too much of it,\Nbut would like to see you be forgiving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any parents. Our only family\Nis you and me, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... but Ayu sometimes thinks...\Nthere was one more family member somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the only siblings. Do you see\Nsomeone in your dream or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a weird feeling, as \Nif it was really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're going to be up early tomorrow\Nbecause we're moving, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get to sleep soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me just a tiny \Nbit more of your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really love stars, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can see way off into the distance\Nwhere people will never reach, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu thinks that is an amazing thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if you keep talking only about\Nthe stars at school, you'll end up getting isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In living my life, a foundation\Nis to liven up the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by talking about what was on TV last night\Ninstead of talk about the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Experience? Foundation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you don't \Nunderstand. Go to sleep soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is an amazingly huge room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can Ayu really use it all \Nalone with Big Brother Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work!\NI may not be much, but allow me to help–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the moving company guys\Nwill do it, so you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could be at least\Nof some assistance, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take their jobs away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Such a way of thinking\Nwas something that Ayu didn't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back at that time, what had happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's something I can't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm going to transfer\Nto Hoshinoumi Academy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um... I'm sorry\Nfor all the things that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until this ability goes away, I can't be authorized\Nto travel to an area with no supervision...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirayanagi, if you could\Ncome see me instead, I'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, that is just too far. At the least,\Ncan it be once a week, and can we alternate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm sorry about that, too.\NI can't come here anymore on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am forced to not mention anything\Nabout this case to others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that I can do about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful for what you have done.\NThat feeling will never waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, I am not dating you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for me to chase you\Nin a one-sided manner is as if I was a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I do feel bad about that.\NHowever, I can't go see you on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. From now on,\Nlet us walk our own separate paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the feeling I have towards you\Nfor saving my life as long as I live. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for saving me.\NI really do appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is where I bid you farewell.\NI hope you stay well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got dumped... me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Excuse me! I've already let myself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough when it's just the two of you, right?\NI came here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are all of you people\Nfrom the same school as Big Brother Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We are from the student council.\NI am Takajo, and this is Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's after school now,\Nwe thought we should help out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unnecessary troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we help you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that would help us out a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How cunning...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we should split up and get things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This must be that delicious thing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that our uncle sent in congratulations\Nthat Ayumi was talking about!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all Kin-san Ramen?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pretend I never saw this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi, can I show you a magic trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that's something I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there. It will only be an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!\NThis is more amazing than the people on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you amused by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't use your ability for play!\NYou've knocked Ayumi out of her wits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to play, \NI'll have you go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah... your big brother is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you're helping us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we shall excuse ourselves here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to go home?\NI'll make dinner so I'd like you to eat that, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough dishes for four.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or so he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haro-haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it is a fad after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Yusa Nishimori,\Nknown as Yusarin. She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think something like this sells...\Nthat's the sign of the apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu's new school is right next to Big Brother Yu's!\NSo she wants to go to school together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'd think I have a \Nsis-com (sister complex).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis-com? Is that some kind of a contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Hoshinoumi Academy...\Nwhat a wonderful name!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a name that sounds like one\Nthat was made just for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That night, I had a dream. I'm sure it was\Nbecause of Ayumi's farfetched announcement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But who was that?{\i0}
